Technical diagram: RAG system architecture with two parallel pipelines. LEFT: Offline Indexing Pipeline - Documents (PDF, DB, HTML icons) -> Loader -> Chunker (scissors icon) -> Embedder (vector icon) -> Vector DB (cylinder icon). RIGHT: Online Runtime Pipeline - User Query -> Embedder -> Vector DB (ANN search arrow) -> Re-Ranker (optional, diamond) -> Context Builder -> LLM -> Structured Output. Clean minimalist style, dark blue/teal color scheme, arrows showing data flow, German labels.